CustomField.description: This field specifies whether duplicate issues are to be tracked or not. If checked, a record will be created each time that a given record is recorded. If unchecked, the system will check to ensure that there are no duplicates.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This field specifies whether duplicate issues are to be tracked or not. If checked, a record will be created each time that a given record is recorded. If unchecked, the system will check to ensure that there are no duplicates.
CustomField.label: Track Duplicates
